{"tid":2423010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中史台] 有無人知，其實關羽同曹操根本就唔係三國時代既武將","createTime":"2021-02-25T15:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T07:59:41.000Z","uid":52658,"like":5,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ab843bc974f33a715c1dacf90175610848cc3f","tid":2423010,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"見到都分唔清東漢末年同三國時代就火刀泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三國時代係220-280年<br />\n曹丕篡漢至西晉滅吳為止<br />\n曹操係220年死 關羽係219年兵敗被殺<br />\n三乜撚野國？<br />\n果陣只有「大漢」同「仲家」兩個國家<br />\n<br />\n即係話 你地好熟悉既三國名將<br />\n曹操關羽呂布董卓袁紹孫策周瑜劉表黃忠呂蒙呢d<br />\n根本就呂係三國時代人物<br />\n呢d係漢人 貨真價實既漢人 清楚未<br />\n<br />\n即係話如果你穿越時空 <br />\n去到袁紹面前話而家係三國時代<br />\n佢會問你「公三小？」然後話你意圖謀反然後誅你三族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時事點：<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">拜登吃屎<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVF6m4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVF6m4y.jpg&h=43b2179b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4e8d165286e78a254de832243592cdd2afd8f9c","tid":2423010,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"五虎大將有兩個唔係唔係三國武將<br />\n五子良將徐晃同樂進唔係<br />\n江表十二虎臣就過半都唔係"},{"pid":"598aa51ab66a9c7782e56bf82128a913ee35e6a4","tid":2423010,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"So?"},{"pid":"824b9324a3d0144ca91d6bccc35493c1aecd557d","tid":2423010,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"598aa51ab66a9c7782e56bf82128a913ee35e6a4","tid":2423010,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"So?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"所以拜登條撚樣咪要死全家<br />\n好合理好公道下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f87016cc72c7b739b09930de0b0fd88a7885601","tid":2423010,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"7500萬人支持川普<br />\n拜登？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJa6naZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJa6naZ.jpg&h=12579019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f62d9381b0958ee5fa80c265c6a147af6bfad4fb","tid":2423010,"uid":74567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"其實袁術都幾撚痴線"},{"pid":"3d413264a0cd38ddec200933824a7e2de34b9480","tid":2423010,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"諸葛亮神機妙算<br />\n周公謹心胸狹窄<br />\n關雲長忠肝義膽<br />\n曹孟德亂世奸雄"},{"pid":"564263bb6e33ae5548bb1a1e19820ed752aca915","tid":2423010,"uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"三國志：蜀書六 <br />\n三國志：魏書一"},{"pid":"891a826be2603e96b817f694942b52ffb6ead821","tid":2423010,"uid":260744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"824b9324a3d0144ca91d6bccc35493c1aecd557d","tid":2423010,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"598aa51ab66a9c7782e56bf82128a913ee35e6a4","tid":2423010,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"So?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"所以拜登條撚樣咪要死全家<br />\n好合理好公道下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"聽落唔係好明，但好似好有料"},{"pid":"71f1d47ac34fecb097e14d5efb89a45fbe36eb2a","tid":2423010,"uid":70769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4e8d165286e78a254de832243592cdd2afd8f9c","tid":2423010,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"五虎大將有兩個唔係唔係三國武將<br />\n五子良將徐晃同樂進唔係<br />\n江表十二虎臣就過半都唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:25:28.000Z","msg":"邊有5虎呢個稱號，演義當中史講？"},{"pid"