先係真正三國時代，至少係222年孫權黃武元年先開始"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"如果咁計 關張馬黃趙得趙雲一個係三國武將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曹丕同劉備都唔係三國人"},{"pid":"6a6d6716687abd36bb74958c0e18bc1e99bf9e7a","tid":2423010,"uid":66514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kg0KdwQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkg0KdwQ.png&h=ac4485e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f511bf90f169d816f1b455e996a2f6020d79328","tid":2423010,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cf4395ed3c75598c10499aae337fff6d00585fe","tid":2423010,"uid":39872,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"關羽=關押習近平2次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"關雲長<br />\n長時間關押馬雲<br />\n<br />\n希望可以抵銷部份影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔駛變關刃或者關刀<br />\nBTW 黑社會拜開關公 會唔會&quot;犯法就係犯法 除非你係XX&quot;所以無事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d62d3825fcccddbf7fbf86fa07d850d20652bf","tid":2423010,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7981e8ae97fd8278d06a7feec8131c3fba78ad15","tid":2423010,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"三國係後世人俾既統稱<br />\n正式學名應該係東漢末年至魏晉南北朝"},{"pid":"3d19568beb87a536d423dc0a5305d8168a94f172","tid":2423010,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7981e8ae97fd8278d06a7feec8131c3fba78ad15","tid":2423010,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"三國係後世人俾既統稱<br />\n正式學名應該係東漢末年至魏晉南北朝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"正式學名其實係魏朝"},{"pid":"b0