0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"正統史學分界係:東漢&gt;曹丕篡漢&gt;魏&gt;司馬炎篡魏&gt;西晉&gt;八王之亂,司馬睿東渡&gt;東晉<br />\n根本就冇三國呢樣野,自然唔會混淆"},{"pid":"423e0c783e46b8b969fb620c60359ebfd11f4099","tid":2423010,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"廣義三國由黃巾開始喎"},{"pid":"f27e654319f679645b3adbebff766d6c16ad8759","tid":2423010,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"423e0c783e46b8b969fb620c60359ebfd11f4099","tid":2423010,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"廣義三國由黃巾開始喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"黃巾開始果時劉備既&quot;國&quot;請問喺邊鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81803d6ef9446d649031b48a2e40049a75143136","tid":2423010,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27e654319f679645b3adbebff766d6c16ad8759","tid":2423010,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"423e0c783e46b8b969fb620c60359ebfd11f4099","tid":2423010,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"廣義三國由黃巾開始喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"黃巾開始果時劉備既&quot;國&quot;請問喺邊鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"咁計係咪得孫權稱帝到鄧艾滅蜀呢段時間叫三國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140c733784dab4b67514c162c30c63d017017926","tid":2423010,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81803d6ef9446d649031b48a2e40049a75143136","tid":2423010,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27e654319f679645b3adbebff766d6c16ad8759","tid":2423010,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"423e0c783e46b8b969fb620c60359ebfd11f4099","tid":2423010,"uid":47470,